<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="BurnLink — Share files. Encrypted. Ephemeral. Files are encrypted in your browser and burned after the first download." />
  <meta name="keywords" content="encrypted file sharing, secure file transfer, e2e encryption, privacy, burnlink" />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0a0a" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="BurnLink — Share files. Encrypted. Ephemeral." />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Share sensitive files securely with end-to-end encryption. One-time download links. No permanent storage." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://burnlink.page" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="BurnLink — Share files. Encrypted. Ephemeral." />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Share files. Encrypted. Ephemeral. One-time links, browser-side encryption, no permanent storage." />
  <title>BurnLink — Share files. Encrypted. Ephemeral.</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: "Inter", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: #0a0a0a; color: #fff; line-height: 1.6; overflow-x: hidden; min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }
    header {
      padding: 1.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
      position: sticky; top: 0; background: #0a0a0a; z-index: 100;
    }
    .header-content { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    .logo { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #ff8c00; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; }
    nav { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; }
    nav a { text-decoration: none; color: #666; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; transition: color 0.2s; }
    nav a:hover, nav a.active { color: #fff; }
    footer { border-top: 1px solid #1e1e1e; padding: 3rem 0; }
    .footer-content { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .footer-section h3 { font-size: 0.68rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #555; }
    .footer-section a { display: block; color: #777; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .footer-section a:hover { color: #fff; }
    .footer-bottom { border-top: 1px solid #1e1e1e; padding-top: 1.5rem; color: #444; font-size: 0.78rem; }
    .error-msg { background: #1a0000; color: #ff6b6b; padding: 0.9rem 1rem; border: 1px solid #2a0000; font-size: 0.88rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav { gap: 1.5rem; }
      .header-content { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; }
      .footer-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
    }
    main { padding: 6rem 0 4rem; min-height: calc(100vh - 140px); }
    .hero { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8rem; align-items: start; }
    .hero-content h1 { font-size: 3.5rem; line-height: 1.05; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -2px; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .hero-content p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #888; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 380px; }
    .features-list { list-style: none; border-top: 1px solid #1e1e1e; }
    .features-list li { padding: 0.85rem 0; font-size: 0.88rem; color: #aaa; border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e1e; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; }
    .features-list li::before { content: ""; display: inline-block; width: 4px; height: 4px; background: #ff8c00; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .upload-section { border: 1px solid #1e1e1e; padding: 2.5rem; }
    .upload-section h2 { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    form { display: grid; gap: 1.25rem; }
    .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
    label { font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #666; }
    input[type="file"], input[type="password"] {
      font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; border: 1px solid #222; background: #111;
      color: #fff; font-family: inherit; transition: border-color 0.2s; min-height: 44px;
      -webkit-appearance: none; appearance: none; border-radius: 0; width: 100%;
    }
    input[type="file"]::file-selector-button {
      cursor: pointer; padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem; background: #1a1a1a; border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
      border-radius: 0; color: #bbb; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 500; margin-right: 0.75rem;
    }
    input[type="password"]::placeholder { color: #444; }
    input[type="file"]:focus, input[type="password"]:focus { outline: none; border-color: #ff8c00; }
    button {
      background: #ff8c00; color: #000; border: none; padding: 0.9rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer; transition: opacity 0.2s; min-height: 44px;
      -webkit-appearance: none; appearance: none; border-radius: 0; width: 100%; font-family: inherit;
    }
    button:hover:not(:disabled) { opacity: 0.85; }
    button:disabled { opacity: 0.4; cursor: not-allowed; }
    .link-box { border: 1px solid #1e1e1e; padding: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    .link-box strong { display: block; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #666; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    #share-link { display: block; word-break: break-all; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; background: #111; border: 1px solid #222; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #ff8c00; text-decoration: none; font-family: "Monaco", "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    .link-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    #copy-link-btn { width: auto; padding: 0.7rem 1.25rem; }
    .status { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #ff8c00; font-weight: 500; }
    .status.error { color: #ff6b6b; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
      .hero-content h1 { font-size: 2.25rem; letter-spacing: -1px; }
      .hero-content p { max-width: 100%; }
      .upload-section { padding: 1.5rem; }
      input[type="file"], input[type="password"] { font-size: 16px; }
      .link-actions { flex-direction: column; }
      #copy-link-btn { width: 100%; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header-content">
        <a href="/" class="logo">BurnLink</a>
        <nav><a href="/" class="active">Home</a><a href="/about">About</a></nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1>Share files.<br>Encrypted.<br>Ephemeral.</h1>
          <p>Files are encrypted in your browser before upload. Links burn after one download. We never see your data.</p>
          <ul class="features-list">
            <li>Browser-side AES-256 encryption</li>
            <li>One-time download links</li>
            <li>Password protection available</li>
            <li>No file stored permanently</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="upload-section">
          <h2>Upload a file</h2>
          <% if (error) { %>
            <p class="error-msg"><%= error %></p>
          <% } %>
          <form id="upload-form" method="post" action="/upload" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="file">Select file</label>
              <input type="file" id="file" name="file" required />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="password">Password (optional)</label>
              <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Leave empty for link-only access" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label>Share mode</label>
              <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem;">
                <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; cursor: pointer; flex: 1;">
                  <input type="radio" name="mode" value="view-once" checked required style="width: 16px; height: 16px;" />
                  <span style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #aaa;">View once (90 sec, no download)</span>
                </label>
                <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; cursor: pointer; flex: 1;">
                  <input type="radio" name="mode" value="download" required style="width: 16px; height: 16px;" />
                  <span style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #aaa;">Download file</span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>
            <button id="upload-btn" type="submit">Encrypt &amp; Upload</button>
            <span id="upload-status" class="status" aria-live="polite"></span>
          </form>
          <div id="link-box" class="link-box" hidden>
            <strong>Your secure link</strong>
            <a id="share-link" href="#"></a>
            <div class="link-actions">
              <button id="copy-link-btn" type="button">Copy link</button>
              <span id="copy-status" class="status" aria-live="polite"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-content">
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3>Product</h3>
          <a href="/">Share files</a>
          <a href="/about">How it works</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3>Resources</h3>
          <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder/BurnLink" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder/BurnLink#readme" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Documentation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3>Developer</h3>
          <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Joy Majumdar</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2026 BurnLink. Share files. Encrypted. Ephemeral.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="/upload.js"></script>
</body>
</html>